INSTALLATION:
Here is what could be done to install this ebuild.
You need to copy this to "/var/lib/layman/cache_***.xml" file.

  <repo quality="experimental" status="unofficial">
    <name><![CDATA[rainyday]]></name>
    <description><![CDATA[overlay for some projects of mine gentoo]]></description>
    <homepage>https://github.com/iegor/rainyday </homepage>
    <owner>
      <email>rmtdev@gmail.com</email>
      <name><![CDATA[Iegor]]></name>
    </owner>
    <source type="git">git://github.com/iegor/rainyday.git </source>
  </repo>

That will make possible to do next
sudo layman -a(--add) rainyday
from your terminal.
